You messed up. The play starts at the beginning of the inning...there's no way a double play here can happen. There are no runners or outs yet!

Can you do it over? Same scenario except Let's make the bases loaded with one out. And change the opponent to the Seattle Mariners. And before the play, can Keith make a comment about the incredible gumption of carnage at second? Ok try again. Thanks!
